OL,3,C'Highly respected' doctor guilty of
OL,4,Csexually abusing female patients
OL,6,FA 'highly respected' doctor has been
OL,7,Fjailed after he was found guilty of
OL,8,Fsexually abusing female patients.
OL,10,FDr Wayne Sefton Davis, 67, carried out
OL,11,Fthe acts, which had "no medical basis"
OL,12,Fagainst the two women during
OL,13,F"invasive" examinations on them during
OL,14,Fthe 1990s and 2000s.
OL,16,FThe Salford GP denied all wrongdoing,
OL,17,Fbut following two trials was convicted
OL,18,Fof indecent assault and sexual assault
OL,19,Fand jailed for eight years.
