OL,3,C'Highly respected' doctor guilty of
OL,4,Csexually abusing female patients
OL,6,FVanessa Thomson, prosecuting, said
OL,7,Fthat Davis' victims were from the
OL,8,FOrthodox Jewish community and "were
OL,9,Fnot brought up learning about sex and
OL,10,Fsexual behaviours at school as might
OL,11,Fbe expected in secular society".
OL,13,FThe women had limited knowledge and
OL,14,Fput their complete trust in a
OL,15,Frespected man they had been told "knew
OL,16,Fbest", which provided "fertile ground"
OL,17,Ffor Dr Davis to abuse each of them.
OL,19,FOne complainant said she went to see
OL,20,Fthe doctor in the 2000s after
OL,21,Fcomplaining of pain in her genitals.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
