OL,3,C'Highly respected' doctor guilty of
OL,4,Csexually abusing female patients
OL,6,FShe claimed the doctor made a "highly
OL,7,Finappropriate comment", before using
OL,8,Fhis fingers to perform an intimate
OL,9,Fexamination.
OL,11,FJurors at Manchester Crown Court were
OL,12,Ftold a gynaecologist said his mode of
OL,13,Fexamination "had no grounding in
OL,14,Fgynaecological practice".
OL,16,FThe court heard after details of Dr
OL,17,FDavis' arrest were published in news
OL,18,Freports, another woman came forward to
OL,19,Freport that she had been abused by him
OL,20,Fin the 1990s.
