OL,3,C'Highly respected' doctor guilty of
OL,4,Csexually abusing female patients
OL,6,FStatements heard in court by the two
OL,7,Fcomplainants indicated they were left
OL,8,Fhumiliated and their experiences
OL,9,Fgreatly affected their trust in people
OL,10,Fespecially doctors.
OL,12,FOne added that her marriage had come
OL,13,Fto an end as a result of the abuse,
OL,14,Fand she had suffered mental, physical
OL,15,Fand emotional pain.
OL,17,FIn brief mitigation, Sarah Elliott KC
OL,18,Fsaid Dr Davis was highly respected in
OL,19,Fthe community. She added that he had
OL,20,Fbeen in custody for over a year since
OL,21,Fthe convictions.
