OL,3,C'Highly respected' doctor guilty of
OL,4,Csexually abusing female patients
OL,6,FJailing Davis for eight years, Judge
OL,7,FPeter Horgan said: "Your convictions
OL,8,Fvividly demonstrate how you abused the
OL,9,Ftrust placed in you by those ladies
OL,10,Fand your community.
OL,12,F"You decided to do what you wanted
OL,13,Fwithout regard."
OL,15,FDr Davis, of Old Hall Road, Salford,
OL,16,Fwas also made subject of the Sex
OL,17,FOffenders Register for life.
