OL,6,F"The CPS worked with Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police to support the women
OL,8,Fthrough the prosecution. We applied to
OL,9,Fthe court for special measures so the
OL,10,Fwomen could give their evidence in the
OL,11,Fbest way for them, so they did not
OL,12,Fhave to face the man who had abused
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"I would like to thank the women for
OL,16,Fsupporting the prosecution and hope
OL,17,Fthey can move forward knowing Davis
OL,18,Fhas now been sentenced.
